Objective

Establish and maintain continuous security governance across FunaFlex’s cloud infrastructure using Prisma Cloud CSPM.
Ensure visibility, compliance, and risk reduction by:

⦁	Enforcing cloud security best practices and compliance standards (e.g., CIS Controls v8.1).
⦁	Coordinating with the IBM Cloud Operations team to evaluate and update configurations, custom policies, and alert rule sets.
⦁	Continuously monitoring and triaging CSPM alerts to identify false positives, operational requirements, and legitimate risks.
⦁	Applying appropriate alert handling actions: dismissal, snooze, exception, or exclusion, and escalating high-risk findings to engineering and application owners for remediation.

The ultimate goal is to reduce *** overall cloud security risk while supporting operational efficiency and audit readiness.

